Is Reese a girl now?

03:49.312 --> 03:50.313
No, Dewey. He's a lady.

03:50.355 --> 03:51.857
Shut up!

03:51.899 --> 03:52.941
Sorry, ma'am.

03:52.983 --> 03:54.151
All right, that's enough.

03:54.193 --> 03:55.861
Reese lost a wrestling match.

03:55.903 --> 03:57.779
It's no big deal--

03:55.903 --> 03:57.779
sometimes you win,

03:57.821 --> 03:59.198
sometimes you don't.

03:59.239 --> 04:00.490
Yeah, son, you have

03:59.239 --> 04:00.490
nothing to be ashamed of.

04:00.532 --> 04:02.283
You did your best.

04:02.325 --> 04:04.953
That girl was just inarguably

04:02.325 --> 04:04.953
